Class DigitalProductProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.digitalservice.properties.ClassificationProperties
      • org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.digitalservice.properties.DigitalProductProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class DigitalProductProperties
extends ClassificationProperties
    DigitalProductProperties describes the properties that describe a digital product. It is typically attached to a solution component, but it can be attached to any referenceable.
